; counter with bad state defined as the max. counter value
; once the bad state is reached after incrementing the counter,
; the system stays in the bad state, i.e., there is no wrap-around
1 sort bitvec 2
2 zero 1
3 state 1
4 init 1 3 2
5 one 1
6 add 1 3 5
8 ones 1
9 sort bitvec 1
10 eq 9 3 8
11 bad 10
12 ite 1 10 3 6
13 next 1 3 12
